Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}osana sugita kanjou jibun nante nakute
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And so time passed, and the more I cried, the more I understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}sou shite toki nagarete naite wa wakatta bun dake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also learned to protect myself and those things I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mamoru koto mo oboeta daiji na mono mo dekite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:24:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'm ignoring someone else's pain so that I can rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.87,0:24:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kitto dareka no itami o mushi shite nari tatteru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In a world that only knows how to take pride in oneself by shaming others.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.13,0:24:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kuraberu koto de shika kagayaku sube o shiranai sekai de
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.47,0:24:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you look up, you'll see the vast universe expanding before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.47,0:24:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}miagereba hora hiroi uchuu ga me no mae ni hirogaru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.81,0:24:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But the rainclouds formed by your tears close up the path that leads to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.81,0:24:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kimi no namida ga tsukuru amagumo sono saki o tozashite shimau
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you cry and the shadows look like they are about to disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kimi ga naite sono kage ga kiesou ni naru toki ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.61,0:24:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become the wind and reflect your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.61,0:24:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}boku wa sou kaze ni natte kimi no kokoro o utsushi dasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.54,0:24:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stir up a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.54,0:24:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}arashi o okoshite